{
  "stem": "18626.7",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 468.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then when it-- morning came, and we start to strain us up, it's like little snow mountains, thousands of them were lifting themselves.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we washed off the snow and we were all shaking, shivering.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were cold, wet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Thin clothes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You know, concentration camp is like clothes, like it's-- it's a shirt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Smoke was going from the human bodies, you know, from the water on the-- on the skin, what you still have left on your bodies.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we were looking around there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They were all on the top, SS troops ready to shoot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Ready to get the order to machine gun.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There was a doctor not far from me, from Lithuania too, Dr.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Blumberg, and his son.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And he was a German Jew, spoke fluently German.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He came to one of the guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he had in his pocket the cross, you know, like a doctors wear.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He took out from his pocket, put it on on his arm.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he came to a guard, lucky.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he says to the German guard, can I take out five prison-- five of the prisoners?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They are about to die if they are not getting a little warmed, a little heat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Please let me take them out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And right near that valley was a-- was a small little farm village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's called Greiling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Greiling near Bad Toelz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The place was Bad Toelz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a place, Bad Toelz, where the German high officers used to come for vacation.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The doctor took five people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then I saw him taken, and he-- I knew him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I says, Dr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Blumberg.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he was afraid because of me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to spoil the thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
